  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<h4>Consumable (Explosive)</h4>\n <p>Grenades can be set to detonate on impact or with a timer that causes them to explode on initiative count 20 (losing all initiative ties). As an action, you can prime and throw a grenade at a point you can see within 30 feet + your Strength modifier x 5. Each creature within 10 feet must make a DC 20 Constitution saving throw. A creature takes [[/r 8d6]] cold damage on a failed save, or half as much as on a successful one. </p>\n<p>Additionally, on a failed save, a creature gains 1 slowed level for 1 minute. At the end of an affected creature's turn, it can repeat this save, ending the effect on a success.</p>\n<p>Â </p>\n<h2>Grenade, cryo</h2>\n<p>Grenades can be set to detonate on impact or with a timer that causes them to explode on initiative count 20 (losing all initiative ties). As an action, you can prime and throw a grenade at a point you can see within 30 feet + your Strength modifier x 5. Each creature within 10 feet must make a DC 14 Constitution saving throw. A creature takes [[/r 2d6]] cold damage on a failed save, or half as much as on a successful one. Additionally, on a failed save, a creature gains 1 slowed level for 1 minute. At the end of an affected creature's turn, it can repeat this save, ending the effect on a success.</p>",
